cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new framework for prototypical learning that utilizes an attention mechanism to determine prototypes. This framework has applications in various areas of computer science such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
